Rating: 4
I've made this twice now and is wonderful!!!!!!!! I ran out of dried cherries and in a pinch, elected to use dried prunes - PERFECTION. I also sprinkled in about a half tablespoon of Grand Marnier - really lovely. You don't have to have pomegranate juice. In another pinch I scooped a heaping teaspoon of blueberry jam. This is really great.

Rating: 4
Just made this for tomorrow night's Seder. It is so good. I used golden raisins instead of dates, but made the rest exactly as written. This will definitely become a regular in years to comes.

